java.lang.Object
dao.Dao
public class Dao

    • getConnection

      public boolean getConnection()
      Basic boolean method for getting Dao connection. Whenever we call Dao method from some other file we must specify which user is using that connection. If the connection is not made it's gonna return null.
      Returns:
      If connection is made it's gonna make this method true. Otherwise it's gonna stay as false and print out the message specified in the code.
